  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Construction of Menstrual Hygiene Toilet for Girls</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Menstruation is considered dirty and impure and during periods. Girls are discouraged to attend school and interested to stay at homes. The unavailability of sanitary pads, inadequate sanitation and absence of separate toilet for girls in schools, Hostels, College compounds. The problem and has a huge impact on girls school attendance and is a major reason for dropouts of girls from schools, Hostels, Colleges, e.t.c.We are ready to construct 25 Toilets for 25 Schools particularly for Girls only.</narrative>
  </description>
